{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/responsive-web-design-v9/workshop-final-exams-table/step-6","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"workshop-final-exams-table","demoType":null,"title":"Korak 6","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Da biste dodali podatke o učeniku u tabelu, moraćete da koristite elemente za red tabele i podatke tabele.</p>\n<p>Element <code>&#x3C;dfn>table data&#x3C;/dfn></code>, <code>td</code>, koristi se za kreiranje ćelije u tabeli.</p>\n<p>Evo primera korišćenja elementa <code>td</code> za tabelu sportista:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-html\">&#x3C;tr>\n  &#x3C;td>1&#x3C;/td>\n  &#x3C;td>John Doe&#x3C;/td>\n  &#x3C;td>USA&#x3C;/td>\n&#x3C;/tr>\n</code></pre>\n<p>Unutar vašeg elementa tela tabele, dodajte element reda tabele, <code>tr</code>, sa tri elementa podataka tabele, <code>td</code>.</p>\n<p>Prvi element podataka tabele treba da sadrži prezime <code>Davis</code>.</p>\n<p>Drugi element podataka tabele treba da sadrži ime <code>Alex</code>.</p>\n<p>Treći element podataka tabele treba da sadrži razred/ocenu <code>54</code>.</p>\n</section>","id":"66a9c14e3b34c719e34bae20","hasEditableBoundaries":true,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":0,"helpCategory":"HTML-CSS","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"responsive-web-design-v9","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":null,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/responsive-web-design-v9/workshop-final-exams-table/step-6"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":true,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"indexhtml","ext":"html","name":"index","contents":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n  <head>\n    <title>Calculus Final Exams Table</title>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\" />\n  </head>\n  <body>\n    <table>\n      <caption>\n        Calculus Final Exam Grades\n      </caption>\n\n      <thead>     \n        <tr>\n          <th>Last Name</th>\n          <th>First Name</th>\n          <th>Grade</th>\n        </tr>\n      </thead>\n\n      <tbody>\n        \n      </tbody>\n    </table>\n  </body>\n</html>","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[21,23],"history":["index.html"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p>Trebalo bi da imate <code>tr</code> element unutar vašeg <code>tbody</code> elementa.</p>","testString":"assert.isNotNull(document.querySelector('tbody tr'));"},{"text":"<p>Trebalo bi da imate element <code>td</code> sa tekstom <code>Davis</code> unutar elementa <code>tr</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(document.querySelector('tbody tr td')?.textContent.trim(), 'Davis');"},{"text":"<p>Trebalo bi da imate element <code>td</code> sa tekstom <code>Alex</code> unutar elementa <code>tr</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(document.querySelectorAll('tbody tr td')[1]?.textContent.trim(), 'Alex');"},{"text":"<p>Trebalo bi da imate element <code>td</code> sa tekstom <code>54</code> unutar elementa <code>tr</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(document.querySelectorAll('tbody tr td')[2]?.textContent.trim(), '54');"},{"text":"<p>Trebalo bi da imate sva tri elementa <code>td</code> unutar elementa <code>tr</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.match(code, /<tr>[\\s\\S]*<td>[\\s\\S]*<\\/td>[\\s\\S]*<td>[\\s\\S]*<\\/td>[\\s\\S]*<td>[\\s\\S]*<\\/td>[\\s\\S]*<\\/tr>/i);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/responsive-web-design-v9/#workshop-final-exams-table","dashedName":"step-6","certification":"responsive-web-design-v9","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"responsive-web-design-v9","chapter":"html","module":"html-forms-and-tables","block":"workshop-final-exams-table","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/responsive-web-design-v9/workshop-final-exams-table/step-7","prevChallengePath":"/learn/responsive-web-design-v9/workshop-final-exams-table/step-5","id":"66a9c14e3b34c719e34bae20","saveSub